# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-02 13:12

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:29
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_0f1c479d:

    # "We get to the theater and get seats in the back."
    "On arrive au cinéma et on s'assoit au fond."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:30
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_29279ffb:

    # rb "So what are we watching anyway?"
    rb "Au fait, on va voir quoi ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:34
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_bb40bd64:

    # rb "Oh yeah?"
    rb "Ah oui ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:36
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_efb601e5:

    # rb "I hope it's the sexy kind. Where they get all sweaty and the lighting is dim, then it pans away right before they start going at it."
    rb "J'espère que c'est un film sexy. Où ils sont tout en sueur et où la lumière est tamisée, puis la caméra s'éloigne juste avant qu'ils ne s'y mettent."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:37
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_516fc9fb:

    # rb "Is it that kind of romantic?"
    rb "C'est ce genre de film romantique ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:38
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_f9e1c11e:

    # pc "Um, I don't know? Maybe?"
    pc "Euh, je sais pas ? Peut-être ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:42
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_e0c6223d:

    # rb "Yeah! Big macho guys with guns and explosions! I love that stuff!"
    rb "Ouais ! Des gros machos avec des flingues et des explosions ! J'adore ce genre de trucs !"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:46
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_832a0115:

    # rb "Oh yeah? I'm not really into scary movies much. They never seem to really be scary to me."
    rb "Ah oui ? Je ne suis pas vraiment fan des films d'horreur. Je ne les trouve jamais vraiment effrayants."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:47
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_10e4b7a7:

    # rb "But I'll give it a try. It'll give me an excuse to cuddle up next to you, at least."
    rb "Mais je vais essayer. Ça me donnera au moins une excuse pour me blottir contre toi."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:51
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_eb93d29d:

    # rb "Oh God, you're going to hear my horse laugh then."
    rb "Oh mon Dieu, tu vas entendre mon rire de cheval alors."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:53
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_6cc4cd44:

    # "There's a little time to chat before the movie starts."
    "On a un peu de temps pour discuter avant que le film commence."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:57
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_592835a4:

    # "Finally the movie starts up and we go silent."
    "Enfin, le film démarre et on se tait."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:59
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_fd60e14c:

    # "She reaches over and holds my hand on top of the arm rest."
    "Elle tend la main et tient la mienne par-dessus l'accoudoir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:60
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_aee76b2d:

    # "The trailers take up about fifteen minutes, then the movie really gets started."
    "Les bandes-annonces durent environ quinze minutes, puis le film commence vraiment."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:62
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_610dce56:

    # "She seems to be liking the movie okay."
    "Elle a l'air d'apprécier le film."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:64
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_1e52f74a:

    # "During the movie, she leans against my shoulder, looking happy, if a little bored."
    "Pendant le film, elle se blottit contre mon épaule, l'air heureuse, même si elle a l'air un peu ennuyée."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:67
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_e7628aae:

    # "Reba really gets into the movie. When there's a big action scene, she's even mimicking punches and cheering at the explosions."
    "Reba est vraiment prise par le film. Lorsqu’il y a une grande scène d’action, elle mime même des coups de poing et applaudit les explosions."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:69
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_8197bbed:

    # "Reba looks bored through most of the movie."
    "Reba a l’air de s’ennuyer pendant la majeure partie du film."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:71
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_2bff2bcf:

    # "She leans against my shoulder and watches silently. Even the jump scares that make me jolt a bit don't seem to have any effect on her."
    "Elle s’appuie contre mon épaule et regarde en silence. Même les sursauts qui me font tressaillir un peu ne semblent avoir aucun effet sur elle."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:74
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_427a223e:

    # "Reba laughs pretty frequently throughout the movie. At first, just little chuckles, but then her laughs turn into loud horse-like whinnies."
    "Reba rit assez souvent tout au long du film. Au début, ce ne sont que de petits gloussements, mais ensuite ses rires se transforment en hennissements bruyants, comme ceux d’un cheval."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:75
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_8c6a087e:

    # "A few of the people in seats nearby turn and look at us."
    "Quelques personnes assises à proximité se retournent et nous regardent."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:76
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_65ecd1be:

    # "I'm a little embarrassed at first, but fuck them, she's having a good time and I love that."
    "Je suis un peu gêné au début, mais qu’ils aillent se faire voir, elle passe un bon moment et j’adore ça."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:79
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_65588a69:

    # rb "That movie was cute. I wish there was a little bit more of the adult stuff in it though, you know?"
    rb "Ce film était mignon. J’aurais aimé qu’il y ait un peu plus de trucs pour adultes dedans, tu vois ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:80
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_73b7e285:

    # rb "Thanks for bringing me."
    rb "Merci de m'avoir emmenée."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:83
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_0ffc7e30:

    # rb "That movie was freaking awesome!"
    rb "Ce film était vraiment génial !"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:85
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_06b31029:

    # rb "Like when he went wham, blam, kapow, krakaTHOOM!"
    rb "Genre quand il a fait « boum, pan, kapow, krakaTHOOM ! »"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:87
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_f9b2297b:

    # rb "I loved it! Thanks for bringing me."
    rb "J'ai adoré ! Merci de m'avoir emmenée."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:90
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_6f921b8c:

    # rb "Wow that was boring. Horror movies just don't do anything for me. Everybody is so dang stupid."
    rb "Ouah, c'était ennuyeux. Les films d'horreur, ça ne me dit vraiment rien. Tout le monde est tellement stupide."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:91
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_a692f6a1:

    # rb "Let's watch something different next time. Horror movies are dumb."
    rb "On regardera autre chose la prochaine fois. Les films d'horreur, c'est nul."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:94
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_4449a4f2:

    # rb "Sorry for laughing so hard. It was really funny though, right?"
    rb "Désolée d'avoir autant ri. C'était vraiment drôle, non ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:95
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_e8d58dda:

    # pc "Yeah it was. Your laugh made me laugh even harder."
    pc "Oui, c'est vrai. Ton rire m'a fait rire encore plus fort."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:96
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_19609177:

    # rb "I know, it's an annoying laugh, but it's mine. Can't do anything for it, ya know?"
    rb "Je sais, c'est un rire agaçant, mais c'est le mien. Je n'y peux rien, tu vois ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:99
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_233f5bf6:

    # "When the credits start rolling, we hang out and chat through them."
    "Quand le générique commence à défiler, on reste là à discuter."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebamoviedate.rpy:103
translate french rebamovietheaterstartdate_029f1c23:

    # "Then when the screen goes black, we walk outside together to my car."
    "Puis, quand l'écran devient noir, on sort ensemble vers ma voiture."

